responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "68789B924EE19874B6ADE281C7530269", "The Godlings, they carry weight of divine will, yes. Their presence ripples, through the currents of spirit. They bring new era, one where old ways, they falter. Spirits urge us... to heed the signs, yes. To find balance in face of change, monumental change. This is why I gather the moot, Godling. To align our tribe with future... not past.")
